<i>adjective</i>: 적합하다 [저카파다], 적당하다 [적땅하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>적합하다 [저카파다]</dt><br>
<dd>fit; adequate</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 조건에 꼭 들어맞아 알맞다.</dd><br>
<dd>Suitable thanks to the quality of fully meeting certain requirements or conditions.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>적당하다 [적땅하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. adequate</dd><br>
<dd>기준, 조건, 정도에 알맞다.</dd><br>
<dd>Meeting requirements or conditions, or being appropriate in terms of degree.</dd><br>
<dd>2. plausible; acceptable</dd><br>
<dd>문제가 되지 않을 정도로 요령이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Tactful enough to avoid causing a problem.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>